# Find the V8 Javascript library.
#
# This module defines
#  V8_FOUND             - True if V8 was found.
#  V8_INCLUDE_DIRS      - Include directories for V8 headers.
#  V8_LIBRARIES         - Libraries for V8.
#
# To specify an additional directory to search, set V8_ROOT.
#
